<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/678014-lately-people-have-been-questioning">lately people have been questioning whether all these memoirs of defectors are completely true... i can&#39;t remember if this author was one of those who admitted that all he had written wasn&#39;t completely honest...has anyone heard about this? I just read &#39;the girl with seven names&#39; and she was interviewed and asked about this....she said there IS a great temptation among defectors to embellish their stories...</a>
</div>
